assert rm_estimator.RM_Estimator(current_weight, current_reps, desired_reps
    ).estimate_weight(base=base) == pytest.approx(expected)
pytest.mark.parametrize(
    'current_weight,current_reps,desired_reps,base,expected', [(150.0, 10, 
    5, 5, 175.0), (150.0, 10, 5, 2.5, 175.0), (150.0, 8, 5, 2.5, 162.5), (
    150.0, 8, 5, 5, 165.0)])
